section.section:
"Qualified candidate" means a teaching candidate who:
Is enrolled in an alternative teacher preparation program;
Intends to teach in a public school in the State in the field of:
Science;
Mathematics; or
Special education;
Has made a commitment to a local board to teach in a public school for at least 3 years; and
Participates in a preresidency internship program for a period of 4 to 8 weeks on or after January 1, 2007.
